  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, you can see Lamborghini cars at several places:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Showroom**: Visit the official Lamborghini dealership in Bangalore, where you can see various models. The dealership staff can provide details on available models and possibly arrange test drives.\n\n2. **Luxury Car Events**: Keep an lookout for automotive events or luxury car exhibitions in the city, where supercars, including Lamborghinis, are often showcased.\n\n3. **Supercar Groups**: Join local automotive or supercar clubs on social media platforms. Members often share information about meet-ups or events where high-end cars like Lamborghinis are present.\n\n4. **Luxury Hotels or Restaurants**: Some luxury hotels or high-end restaurants in Bangalore attract owners of exotic cars. Visiting such places might give you a chance to spot a Lamborghini parked outside.\n\n5. **Public Roads**: Occasionally, Lamborghinis can be spotted on the roads of Bangalore, especially in affluent neighborhoods or during car rallies.\n\nAlways check for any local events or dealer promotions for more specific opportunities to see these luxury cars.",
